long_description: beautifully crafted event spaces with cutting-edge technology and urban eclectic interiors located in the heart of jakarta. there are 2 iconic spaces that are suitable for corporate gatherings, press conferences, presentations, and awarding nights. whether you are launching new products, displaying artwork, or conducting live performances, you will be able to bring your event to life in a bold way with the help of state-of-the-art technology, and in-house catering and support staff. our main hall; sekar jagad hall is located in thamrin, can hold 300-400 people featuring urban industrial interior, cutting-edge technology, a concert-grade sound system, and impressive lighting options. our second space, located in the kelapa gading area, is called mentawai hall by kriya featuring a striking 224-seat auditorium equipped with a professional sound system, a large led screen, and timeless interiors. several of our past events including: - wedding - seminar and training- press conference- fashion show- concert & mini concert- product launching- awarding night- religious services
